        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3 mt-8">What Houston Fire Department Inspectors Look For</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">The Houston Fire Department conducts commercial property inspections that always include fire extinguisher compliance checks. Common violations cited in Houston properties:</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 mb-8">
