            { q: 'What happens if my Houston business fails a fire extinguisher inspection?', a: 'You receive a Notice of Violation with typically 30 days to correct. Uncorrected violations carry fines starting at $500/day per violation. The Houston Fire Department can issue occupancy restrictions for serious deficiencies.' },
